"title": "8436: giving, of possessions",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8436: giving, of possessions",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Making one's possession available for God's service in the way in which he directs, as a practical recognition that all possessions come from him.</p>\n<h2>Ministries that require the giving of material possessions</h2>\n<h3>The relief of the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">PRO 28:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:25\">LEV 25:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7-Deut15:8\">DEU 15:7–15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:7\">ISA 58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:10\">GAL 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>The support of God's servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:48\">NUM 3:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:9\">NUM 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:8-2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:8–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:10\">MAT 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:15-Phil4:18\">PHP 4:15–4:18</a></p>\n<h3>The care of widows and orphans</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:12\">DEU 26:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:5-Ruth2:12\">RUT 2:5–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:3-1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:3–5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Motives for the giving of material possessions</h2>\n<h3>Obedience to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:7\">2CO 9:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:11-Exod30:16\">EXO 30:11–30:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:6-Lev12:8\">LEV 12:6–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:28\">DEU 14:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:8-Mal3:10\">MAL 3:8–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:25\">LUK 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:6-Rom13:7\">ROM 13:6–13:7</a></p>\n<h3>Gratitude for God's generosity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:14\">1CH 29:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:20-Gen28:22\">GEN 28:20–28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:9-Deut26:10\">DEU 26:9–26:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:27-1Sam1:28\">1SA 1:27–1:28</a></p>\n<h3>Love for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:15\">2CH 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:9-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:9–7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:33-Luke10:35\">LUK 10:33–10:35</a></p>\n<h2>The manner of giving material possessions</h2>\n<h3>Willingly and cheerfully</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:8\">MAT 10:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:2\">EXO 25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5\">EXO 35:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:4\">2KI 12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:6\">1CH 29:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:17\">1CH 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:10\">2CH 24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:7-2Chr35:9\">2CH 35:7–35:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:28\">EZR 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:11-2Cor8:12\">2CO 8:11–8:12</a></p>\n<h3>Unostentatiously</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:1-Matt6:4\">MAT 6:1–6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Regularly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:2\">1CO 16:2</a></p>\n<h3>Generously</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:5\">EXO 36:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:13\">NUM 7:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:3-1Chr29:4\">1CH 29:3–29:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:38\">LUK 6:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:2-2Cor8:3\">2CO 8:2–8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></p>\n<h2>God measures his people's giving</h2>\n<h3>With a reckoning different from the world's</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:8\">2CH 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">MRK 12:41–12:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a></p>\n<h3>With regard for people's capacity to give</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:30\">LEV 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:8\">LEV 27:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:17\">DEU 16:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29\">ACT 11:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:12\">2CO 8:12</a></p>\n<h2>God rewards the giver appropriately</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:18-Phil4:19\">PHP 4:18–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:10\">2CH 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:25\">PRO 11:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:9\">PRO 22:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">PRO 28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:1\">ECC 11:1</a> <em>encouragement to be enterprising in giving</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:10\">ISA 58:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:42\">MAT 10:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:34–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:9\">LUK 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:35\">ACT 20:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6\">2CO 9:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's reward overwhelming the giver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">PRO 3:9–3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:38\">LUK 6:38</a></p>\n<h2>God's giving: the model for his people's giving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:8\">MAT 10:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:8-2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:8–8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:15</a></p>",
